The paper discusses the implementation of a software framework that combines Component-Based Software Engineering and Agent-Oriented Software Engineering, drawing inspiration from hybrid agent control architectures. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including software engineering (cs.SE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), distributed computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and programming languages (cs.PL). However, given that the paper focuses on the development of a software framework, cs.SE is the most likely sub-category.
